agency%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBar%2C%20meant%20to%20end%20his%20tenure%20only%20next%20year%2C%20was%20appointed%20Shin%20Bet%20chief%20in%20October%202021%20by%20the%20previous%20Israeli%20government%20that%20briefly%20forced%20Netanyahu%20from%20power%20between%20June%202021%20and%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20relations%20with%20Netanyahu%20were%20strained%20even%20before%20the%20unprecedented%20October%20Hamas%20attack%20which%20sparked%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20notably%20over%20proposed%20judicial%20reforms%20that%20had%20split%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20worsened%20after%20the%20March%204%20release%20of%20the%20internal%20Shin%20Bet%20report%20on%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20acknowledged%20the%20agency's%20own%20failure%20in%20preventing%20the%20attack%2C%20but%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Ba%20policy%20of%20quiet%20had%20enabled%20Hamas%20to%20undergo%20massive%20military%20buildup%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBar%20had%20already%20hinted%20that%20he%20would%20resign%20before%20the%20end%20of%20his%20term%2C%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20his%20agency's%20failure%20to%20prevent%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecret%20motives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBar's%20dismissal%20provoked%20the%20anger%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20led%20to%20demonstrations%20accusing%20Netanyahu%20of%20threatening%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20thousand%20people%20braved%20bad%20weather%20late%20Thursday%20to%20demonstrate%20outside%20Netanyahu's%20private%20residence%20in%20Jerusalem%20and%20then%20the%20Israeli%20parliament%2C%20where%20ministers%20were%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20made%20public%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Bar%20said%20Netanyahu's%20arguments%20were%20%26quot%3Bgeneral%2C%20unsubstantiated%20accusations%20that%20seem%20to%20hide%20the%20motivations%20behind%20the%20decision%20to%20terminate%20(his)%20duties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wro