onus%20points%20system%20during%20its%20board%20meeting%20in%20April%20which%20could%20give%20more%20weightage%20to%20bigger%20victories%2C%20especially%20overseas%2C%20during%20the%20next%20World%20Test%20Championship%20cycle.%20The%202025-27%20WTC%20cycle%20will%20begin%20with%20India's%20five-match%20away%20Test%20series%20against%20England%20in%20June.%20As%20per%20the%20prevailing%20rules%2C%20the%20team%20winning%20by%20the%20smallest%20margin%20or%20by%20an%20innings%20gets%2012%20points%2C%20six%20points%20for%20a%20tie%20and%20four%20points%20for%20a%20draw.%20But%20this%20could%20see%20a%20change%20as%20the%20global%20governing%20body%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20Telegraph%2C%20is%20considering%20awarding%20bonus%20points%20for%20innings%20victories%20or%20for%20a%20win%20above%20a%20certain%20big%20margin%20such%20as%20100%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20issues%20such%20as%20giving%20bonus%20points%20for%20innings%20wins%20etc%20has%20been%20in%20continuous%20discussion%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20WTC%2C%20as%20many%20teams%20felt%20that%20due%20weight%20is%20not%20getting%20for%20wins%20against%20big%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20development%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20such%20topics%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20discussions%2C%20and%20this%20could%20again%20come%20up%20for%20deliberations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20could%20now%20change%20as%20the%20ICC%20might%20bring%20in%20bonus%20points%20for%20landslide%20wins%2C%20and%20extra%20points%20could%20be%20given%20to%20victories%20over%20frontline%20teams%20such%20as%20India%2C%20Australia%20and%20England%2C%20as%20per%20their%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYeah%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20move%20if%20it%20really%20happens.%20The%20teams%20will%20be%20more%20motivated%20to%20go%20for%20results%2C%20as%20we%20could%20see%20some%20exciting%20games%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20former%20India%20player%20told%20PTI%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20is%20also%20mulling%20giving%20extra%20points%20for%20wins%20away%20from%20home.%20%E2%80%9CYeah%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20motivating%20factor%20for%2C%20you%20know%2C%20those%20%E2%80%98smaller'%20teams%2C%20Look%2C%20when%20New%20Zealand%20beat%20India%20last%20year%2C%20it%20was%20a%20historic%20win%20for%20them%20as%20not%20many%20teams%20came%20here%20and%20beat%20us.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20got%20any%20extra%20points%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20winning%20away%20from%20home%20in%20itself%20can%20act%20as%20a%20motivating%20factor%2C%20now%20the%20teams%20will%20have%20that%20carrot%20in%20front%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20extra%20points%2C%20if%20it%20really%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20the%20ICC%20board%20meeting%20might%20also%20consider%20the%20two-tier%20Test%20system%2C%20which%20is%20vocally%20supported%20by%20Cricket%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20needs%20a%20lot%20of%20discussion%20before%20putting%20into%20practice%20as%20some%20teams%20might%20feel%20deprived%20of%20regular%20chances%20to%20play%20against%20strong%20teams%20like%20India%20or%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20it%20is%2C%20series%20between%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%20or%20Australia%20and%20West%20Indies%20are%20less%20in%20numbers%20compared%20to%20series%20between%20top%20teams%20in%20a%20WTC%20cycle.%20So%2C%20they%20should%20think%20about%20it%20a%20lot%20before%20implementing%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20player%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742521500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4dlth3ro_team-india-test_625x300_27_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ficc-considers-mammoth-changes-to-point-system-for-world-test-championship-2025-27-cycle-7966773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20is%