urt%20ordered%20Mr%20Suri%20%26quot%3Bshall%20not%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20United%20States%20unless%20and%20until%20the%20court%20issues%20a%20contrary%20order.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20(ACLU)%2C%20which%20has%20also%20filed%20an%20emergency%20motion%20to%20stop%20the%20deportation%2C%20said%20Mr%20Suri%20was%20being%20held%20at%20an%20immigration%20detention%20center%20in%20Louisiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRipping%20someone%20from%20their%20home%20and%20family%2C%20stripping%20them%20of%20their%20immigration%20status%2C%20and%20detaining%20them%20solely%20based%20on%20political%20viewpoint%20is%20a%20clear%20attempt%20by%20President%20Trump%20to%20silence%20dissent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20ACLU%20immigrant%20rights%20attorney%20Sophia%20Gregg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20patently%20unconstitutional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20French%20government%20condemned%20the%20expulsion%20of%20a%20French%20space%20scientist%20meant%20to%20attend%20a%20conference%20in%20Houston%20after%20officials%20searched%20his%20smartphone%20and%20found%20what%20they%20called%20%26quot%3Bhateful%26quot%3B%20messages%20against%20US%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDr%20Khan%20Suri%20is%20an%20Indian%20national%20who%20was%20duly%20granted%20a%20visa%20to%20enter%20the%20United%20States%20to%20continue%20his%20doctoral%20research%20on%20peacebuilding%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%26quot%3B%20Georgetown%20University%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20him%20engaging%20in%20any%20illegal%20activity%2C%20and%20we%20have%20not%20received%20a%20reason%20for%20his%20detention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20%26quot%3Bnor%20any%20other%20government%20official%20has%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Suri%20has%20committed%20any%20crime%20or%2C%20indeed%2C%20broke%20any%20law%20whatsoever%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20lawyer%20said%20in%20the%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20accused%20the%20US%20government%20of%20having%20detained%20Mr%20Suri%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20his%20family%20connection%20and%20constitutionally%20protected%20free%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFellow%20arrested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Suri%20--%20a%20fellow%20at%20Georgetown's%20Alwaleed%20Bin%20Talal%20Center%20for%20Muslim-Christian%20Understanding%2C%20according%20to%20the%20university%20website%20--%20was%20arrested%20Monday%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Arlington%2C%20Virginia%2C%20according%20to%20Politico%2C%20which%20first%20reported%20on%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETricia%20McLaughlin%2C%20a%20spokeswoman%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%2C%20said%20on%20X%20that%20Mr%20Suri%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20foreign%20exchange%20student%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20actively%20spreading%20Hamas%20propaganda%20and%20promoting%20anti-Semitism%20on%20social%20media.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcLaughlin%20accused%20him%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bclose%20connections%20to%20a%20known%20or%20suspected%20terrorist%2C%20who%20is%20a%20senior%20advisor%20to%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20decided%20the%20researcher%20was%20subject%20to%20deportation%20under%20a%20provision%20of%20immigration%20law%20that%20allows%20for%20expulsion%20if%20the%20visa%20holder's%20presence%20in%20the%20United%20States%20is%20determined%20to%20threaten%20US%20foreign%20policy%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20a%20US-designated%20terror%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeorgetown%20University%20said%20it%20backs%20its%20%26quot%3Bcommunity%20members'%20rights%20to%20free%20and%20open%20inquiry%2C%20deliberation%20and%20debate%2C%20even%20if%20the%20underlying%20ideas%20may%20be%20difficult%2C%20controversial%20or%20objectionable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Mr%20Suri's%20lawyer%2C%20Politico%20reported%20that%20Mr%20Suri's%20wife%20is%20a%20US%20citizen%20of%20Palestinian%20descent%2C%20and%20that%20the%20couple%20believes%20they%20are%20being%20targeted%20because%20the%20government%20suspects%20they%20oppose%20US%20policy%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742521320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fs4f5t32g_badar-khan-suri_625x300_20_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbadar-khan-suri-deportation-news-us-judge-blocks-indian-researchers-deportation-over-alleged-hamas-ties-7972781%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20judge%20ordered%20Thursday%20that%20an%20Indian%20researcher%20at%20a%20top%20American%20university%20not%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20country%2C%20following%20his%20arrest%20and%20threat%20of%20expulsion%20for%20alleged%20Hamas%20ties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSeparated%20In%202022%26quot%3B%3A%20Chahal-Dhanashree%20Divorce%20Petition's%20Big%20Revelation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20family%20court%20on%20Thursday%20allowed%20the%20joint%20plea%20filed%20by%20cricketer%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20and%20his%20estranged%20wife%20seeking%20divorce%20by%20mutual%20consent.%20The%20estranged%20couple%20appeared%20before%20the%20family%20court%20in%20Bandra.%20Chahal's%20advocate%20Nitin%20Gupta%20said%20the%20family%20court%20has%20granted%20decree%20on%20the%20joint%20petition%20filed%20by%20Chahal%20and%20Verma%20for%20divorce%20by%20mutual%20consent.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20parties%20have%20complied%20with%20the%20consent%20terms.%20%26quot%3BThe%20family%20court%20has%20accepted%20th