rom%20the%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20schoolchildren%20sitting%20at%20desks%20set%20up%20in%20the%20East%20Room%20of%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20smiled%20as%20held%20up%20the%20order%20after%20signing%20it%20at%20a%20special%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20the%20order%20would%20%26quot%3Bbegin%20eliminating%20the%20federal%20Department%20of%20Education%20once%20and%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20shut%20it%20down%20and%20shut%20it%20down%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20It's%20doing%20us%20no%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20return%20education%20back%20to%20the%20states%20where%20it%20belongs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%2C%20created%20in%201979%2C%20cannot%20be%20shuttered%20without%20the%20approval%20of%20Congress%20--%20but%20Trump's%20order%20will%20likely%20have%20the%20power%20to%20starve%20it%20of%20funds%20and%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20honors%20one%20of%20Trump's%20campaign%20promises%20and%20is%20among%20the%20most%20drastic%20steps%20yet%20in%20the%20brutal%20overhaul%20of%20the%20government%20that%20Trump%20is%20carrying%20out%20with%20the%20help%20of%20tech%20tycoon%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20directs%20Education%20Secretary%20Linda%20McMahon%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20all%20necessary%20steps%20to%20facilitate%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20and%20return%20education%20authority%20to%20the%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20and%20educators%20have%20slammed%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20Democrat%20in%20the%20Senate%2C%20Chuck%20Schumer%2C%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btyrannical%20power%20grab%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20destructive%20and%20devastating%20steps%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20ever%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublican%20leaders%2C%20including%20governors%20Ron%20DeSantis%20of%20Florida%20and%20Greg%20Abbott%20of%20Texas%2C%20were%20in%20the%20audience%20for%20the%20signing%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20cast%20the%20move%20as%20necessary%20to%20save%20money%20and%20improve%20educational%20standards%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20claiming%20they%20are%20lagging%20behind%20those%20in%20Europe%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20education%20has%20been%20a%20battleground%20for%20decades%20in%20America's%20culture%20wars%2C%20and%20Republicans%20have%20long%20wanted%20to%20remove%20control%20of%20it%20from%20the%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Beautiful%20day'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20appointment%20of%20McMahon%20--%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20World%20Wrestling%20Entertainment%20--%20to%20lead%20the%20department%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20sign%20that%20its%20days%20were%20numbered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20said%20at%20the%20signing%20ceremony%20that%20%26quot%3Bhopefully%20she%20will%20be%20our%20last%20secretary%20of%20education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcMahon%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20halve%20the%20department's%20staff%20after%20being%20sworn%20in%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20White%20House%20that%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20get%20those%20dollars%20back%20to%20the%20states%20without%20the%20bureaucracy%20of%20Washington.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20promised%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20department%20and%20devolve%20its%20powers%20to%20US%20states%2C%20in%20much%20the%20same%20way%20that%20has%20happened%20with%20abortion%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20White%20House%20said%20earlier%20that%20a%20rump%20education%20department%20was%20likely%20to%20stay%20on%20to%20deal%20with%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20functions%26quot%3B%20including%20loans%20and%20some%20grants%20for%20low-income%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20will%20be%20much%20smaller%20than%20it%20is%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Press%20Secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20told%20reporters%20before%20the%20signing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Heritage%20Foundation%20--%20a%20right-wing%20think-tank%20that%20has%20seen%20many%20of%20its%20%26quot%3BProject%202025%26quot%3B%20recommendations%20adopted%20by%20Trump%20--%20welcomed%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20beautiful%20day%20to%20dismantle%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%20the%20US%20government%20has%20had%20a%20limited%20role%20in%20education%2C%20with%20only%20about%2013%20percent%20of%20funding%20for%20primary%20and%20secondary%20schools%20coming%20from%20federal%20coffers%2C%20the%20rest%20being%20funded%20by%20states%20and%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20federal%20funding%20is%20invaluable%20for%20low-income%20schools%20and%20students%20with%20special%20needs.%20And%20the%20federal%20government%20has%20been%20essential%20in%20enforcing%20key%20civil%20rights%20protections%20for%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20his%20billionaire%20advisor%20Musk%20and%20Musk's%20Department%20for%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%20have%20already%20dismantled%20several%20other%20government%20agencies%2C%20effectively%20crippling%20them%20by%20slashing%20programs%20and%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20move%20to%20dismantle%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20was%20halted%20earlier%20this%20week%20by%20a%20federal%20judge%2C%20who%20said%20the%20push%20likely%20violated%20the%20US%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742519400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fnbhml5c_donald-trump_625x300_21_March_2