o-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrench%20Polynesia%20had%20been%20on%20my%20bucket%20list%3C%2Fa%3E%20ever%20since%20I%20learned%20of%20its%20existence%2C%20and%20last%20August%2C%20I%20finally%20made%20it%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20spent%2016%20days%20traveling%20across%20this%20dreamy%20French%20overseas%20territory.%20Our%20itinerary%20included%20six%20islands%20in%20the%20Society%20Islands%20archipelago%2C%20a%20region%20that's%20part%20of%20French%20Polynesia's%20118%20Pacific%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20during%20the%20high%20season%2C%20but%20it%20never%20felt%20crowded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20islands%20are%20as%20stunning%20as%20their%20reputation%2C%20with%20pristine%20white-sand%20beaches%20and%20vivid%20turquoise%20lagoons.%20I%20loved%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-save-on-french-polynesia-travel-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20French%20Polynesia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20there%20are%20five%20things%20I'd%20have%20done%20differently%20to%20make%20it%20even%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Houses%20on%20stilts%20in%20Moorea%2C%20French%20Polynesia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dbc81f69253ccddf99c82c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFerries%20were%20reliable%20and%20cheaper%20for%20short%20routes%20like%20Tahiti%20to%20Moorea%20(pictured).%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ebbffa5-d470-42a8-a326-506b6e98607b%5C%22%3E1.%20Research%20the%20best%20way%20to%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20too%20much%20time%20planning%20flights%20between%20islands%20when%20I%20should%20have%20first%20studied%20a%20map%20of%20the%20Society%20Islands%20to%20see%20which%20routes%20were%20better%20by%20ferry.%20I%20also%20should%20have%20ignored%20most%20of%20the%20options%20on%20the%20cluttered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-tahiti-nui-french-polynesia-papeete-paris-seattle-us-airline-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20Tahiti%3C%2Fa%3E%20website%20%E2%80%94%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airtahiti.com%2Fen%2Fbook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBook%3C%2Fa%3E%20feature%20is%20all%20that's%20needed%20for%20flight%20times%20and%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFerries%20proved%20to%20be%20reliable%2C%20comfortable%2C%20and%20much%20cheaper%20for%20short%20routes%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-underrated-places-to-visit-frequent-traveler-80-countries-2024-7%23there-was-so-much-to-see-on-the-marquesas-islands-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETahiti%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Moorea%20and%20Huahine-Raiatea-Taha'a-Bora%20Bora.%20Knowing%20that%20earlier%20would%20have%20saved%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20planning%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20islands%2C%20like%20Taha'a%2C%20don't%20even%20have%20an%20airport.%20Often%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BVanilla%20Island%2C%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20its%20fragrant%20plantations%2C%20it's%20only%20accessible%20by%20boat%20via%20Raiatea%20%E2%80%94%20either%20a%2045-minute%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapetahiexpress.pf%2Fen%2Fhome%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApetahi%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%20ferry%20or%20a%2030-minute%20water%20taxi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20glad%20we%20made%20it%20there%20because%20it's%20where%20we%20had%20one%20of%20our%20most%20magical%20experiences%20%E2%80%94%20swimming%20with%20six%20manta%20rays%20in%20the%20open%20ocean%2C%20completely%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swimming%20with%20manta%20rays%20in%20French%20Polynesia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dbcfabb8b41a9673fb2ecb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20swam%20with%20six%20manta%20rays%20in%20Taha'a.%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20routes%2C%20flights%20are%20the%20better%20choice.%20We%20took%20the%20Maupiti%20Express%202%20ferry%20from%20Bora%20Bora%20to%20Maupiti%20since%20no%20flights%20fit%20our%20schedule%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20do%20it%20again.%20It's%20less%20comfortable%2C%20and%20the%20rough%20two-and-a-half-hour%20ride%20is%20only%20for%20the%20strongest%20stomachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20by%20plane%20or%20ferry%2C%20checking%20schedules%20before%20booking%20accommodations%20is%20key.%20Ferries%20don't%20run%20daily%2C%20and%20flight%20prices%20can%20fluctuate%20wildly%20%E2%80%94%20one%20ticket%20we%20saw%20was%20%24120%20on%20Monday%20but%20%24327%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlanning%20around%20these%20factors%20made%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20our%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ccb6d3df-2088-4d5e-acba-1be95a765906%5C%22%3E2.%20Keep%20the%20time%20change%20in%20mind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20tripped%20up%20by%20the%20time%20change%20when%20flying%20east%20into%20Tahiti.%20Since%20we%20traveled%20through%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20we%20essentially%20went%20back%20in%20time%2C%20landing%20a%20day%20before%20our%20departure%20date.%20The%20final%20leg%20of%20our%20journey%20left%20Auckland%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20August%2017%20and%20arrived%20in%20Papeete%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20August%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mistakenly%20booked%20our%20hotel%20in%20Papeete%20for%20the%20wrong%20date%2C%20assuming%20we%20would%20arrive%20on%20the%2017th.%20Fortunately%2C%20this%20mix-up%20is%20so%20common%20that%20Booking.com%20sent%20a%20message%20double-checking%20the%20date%2C%20allowing%20me%20to%20correct%20the%20mistake%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poisson%20cru%2C%20a%20local%20coconut%20milk%20ceviche%2C%20in%20French%20Polynesia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%2