%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThen%20she%20started%20getting%20serious%20with%20one%20particular%20woman.%20This%20violated%20our%20rules%2C%20but%20we%20had%20a%20long%20talk%20about%20it%2C%20and%20I%20agreed%20to%20it.%20Soon%20this%20woman%20began%20coming%20around%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20then%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20she%20came%20over%20again.%20Except%20this%20time%2C%20she%20stayed.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe's%20been%20here%20ever%20since%20%E2%80%94%20eating%20our%20food%2C%20using%20our%20utilities%2C%20watching%20our%20streaming%20channels%2C%20and%20contributing%20nothing.%20I%20resent%20the%20financial%20aspect%20of%20this%2C%20but%20honestly%2C%20most%20of%20my%20resentment%20is%20due%20to%20her%20presence%20in%20my%20life%20period.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20talk%20to%20my%20wife%20about%20this%3F%20I%20agreed%20to%20everything%20up%20to%20this%20point%20because%20I%20love%20her%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20lose%20her.%20But%20I%20can't%20afford%20to%20financially%20support%20another%20grown%20adult.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBad%20at%20Boundaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Bad%20at%20Boundaries%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20say%20that%20your%20wife's%20lover%20spent%20the%20night%20and%20never%20left.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20optimistic%20of%20me%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20necessarily%20means%20she's%20moved%20in.%20As%20long%20as%20her%20prior%20living%20situation%20remains%20stable%20and%20available%2C%20I%20think%20you%20can%20approach%20this%20situation%20in%20the%20way%20it%20has%20been%20presented%20to%20you%3A%20a%20really%20long%20slumber%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20paying%20resident%20of%20your%20home%2C%20you%20have%20every%20right%20to%20pull%20your%20wife%20aside%20and%20tell%20her%20it's%20time%20to%20wrap%20up%20this%20party.%20Or%20at%20least%20ask%20her%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20situation%20so%20that%20you%20can%20put%20some%20parameters%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20I'm%20not%20an%20expert%20on%20polyamorous%20or%20open%20relationships%2C%20so%20I%20discussed%20your%20dilemma%20with%20Janet%20Hardy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20foremost%20authorities%20on%20the%20topic.%20Hardy%20is%20a%20writer%2C%20educator%2C%20and%20the%20coauthor%20of%20over%20a%20dozen%20books%20on%20sexualities%20and%20relationships%2C%20including%20the%20cultural%20phenomenon%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ethical%20Slut%3A%20A%20Practical%20Guide%20to%20Polyamory%2C%20Open%20Relationships%2C%20and%20Other%20Freedoms%20in%20Sex%20and%20Love%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20read%20your%20letter%20to%20Hardy%2C%20not%20only%20did%20she%20have%20wonderful%20insight%20to%20offer%2C%20but%20she's%20also%20been%20in%20a%20similar%20situation.%20She%20called%20her%20experience%20in%20this%20area%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20hardest%20times%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20marriage.%20So%2C%20you're%20not%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae850105-3494-41de-afd7-b7722ab87866%5C%22%3ESet%20boundaries%20around%20tangible%20behaviors%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHardy's%20first%20observation%20after%20hearing%20your%20story%20was%20that%20you%20and%20your%20wife%20made%20a%20common%20beginner's%20mistake%3A%20You%20agreed%20not%20to%20let%20potential%20outside%20relationships%20get%20too%20serious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHardy%20explained%20that%20feelings%20are%20difficult%20things%20to%20control%2C%20so%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20create%20rules%20around%20intangibles%20such%20as%20feelings%2C%20it's%20important%20for%20couples%20who%20are%20planning%20to%20open%20up%20their%20relationships%20to%20establish%20ground%20rules%20around%20tangible%20behaviors%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHardy%20listed%20a%20few%20examples%3A%20Set%20time%20periods%20for%20the%20original%20couple%20to%20spend%20together%2C%20specify%20limits%20for%20time%20spent%20with%20outside%20partners%2C%20and%20reserve%20some%20experiences%20for%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fef03042-1ba8-409c-8955-a62576ad77a7%5C%22%3ESet%20an%20appointment%20to%20talk%20things%20over%20with%20your%20partner%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20you%20can%20put%20boundaries%20around%20tangible%20things%20going%20forward%2C%20for%20now%2C%20what's%20done%20is%20done.%20And%20Hardy%20was%20adamant%20that%20your%20situation%20must%20be%20dealt%20with%20swiftly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Hardy%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BTwo%20people%20who%20don't%20like%20one%20another%20living%20under%20the%20same%20roof%20is%20an%20explosive%20situation.%26quot%3B%20That%20said%2C%20she%20encouraged%20you%20to%20refrain%20from%20addressing%20the%20situation%20during%20a%20fight%20when%20tensions%20are%20running%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20ahead%20of%20the%20explosion%20by%20setting%20an%20appointment%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue.%20Initially%2C%20you%20should%20address%20the%20situation%20with%20your%20wife%2C%20not%20her%20lover.%20Make%20sure%20you%20both%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%20and%20really%20listen%20to%20what%20the%20other%20has%20to%20say.%20Talking%20sticks%20might%20sound%20cheesy%2C%20but%20they%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20meeting%20shouldn't%20be%20limited%20to%20troubleshooting%20the%20issue%20of%20your%20new%20roommate.%20Schedule%20regular%20check-ins%2C%20and%2C%20if%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20you%20can%20accept%20your%20wife's%20new%20lover%20as%20a%20long-term%20addition%20to%20your%20life%2C%20bring%20them%20into%20these%20conversations%20as%20well.%20In%20fact%2C%20if%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20Hardy%20suggests%20you%20each%20have%20individual%20check-ins%20with%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20will%20depend%20on%20what%20you%20and%20your%20wife%20decide%20about%20her%20lover%20moving%20into%20your%20home%20full-time.%20If%20you%20agree%20to%20a%20family-style%20poly%20relationship%2C%20treat%20it%20like%20a%20family.%20But%20if%20you%20decide%20you're%20more%20comfortable%20keeping%20outside%20intimate%20relationships%20compartmentalized%2C%20they%20need%20to%20stay%20compartmentalized.%20Whichever%20you%20and%20your%20wife%20choose%2C%20Hardy%20says%20it%20must%20be%20built%20on%20those%20tangible%20goals%20I%20mentioned%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Hardy's%20case%2C%20she%20was%20in%20your%20wife's%20position.%20Her%20adult%20child%20needed%20help%2C%20so%2C%20without%20asking%20her%20partner%2C%20she%20let%20her%20son%20move%20into%20her%20and%20her%20partner's%20already%20cramped%20space.%20Her%20partner%20was%2C%20like%20you%2C%20understandably%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20successfully%20navigate%20the%20situation%2C%20Hardy's%20partner%20told%20her%20what%20he%20needed%20from%20her.%20Things%20like%20%26quot%3BI%20need%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20time%20for%20just%20us.%26quot%3B%20But%20such%20clear%20parameters%20require%20honesty.%20For%20you%2C%20this%20will%20mean%20getting%20familiar%20with%20the%20feelings%20sitting%20just%20beneath%20your%20resentment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20sure%2C%20paying%20for%20another%20adult's%20bills%20against%20your%20will%20is%20a%20justifiable%20complaint%20%E2%80%94%20a%20complaint%20you%20should%20address%20by%20charging%20your%20new%20roomie%20rent%20at%20the%20very%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20admitted%20that%20your%20feelings%20go%20beyond%20money%2C%20and%20it's%20imperative%20that%20you%20understand%20these%20feelings%20so%20you%20can%20turn%20them%20into%20a%20list%20of%20things%20you%20need%20to%20feel%20satisfied%20within%20your%20relationship.%20Then%20communicate%20these%20needs%20to%20your%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20you%20need%20more%20affirmation%20and%20attention%2C%20or%20maybe%20you%20simply%20need%20your%20wife's%20lover%20to%20go%20home.%20This%20is%20what%20Hardy's%20partner%20ultimately%20required%2C%20and%20the%20solution%20to%20her%20dilemma%20meant%20her%20son%20getting%20his%20own%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20lose%20your%20wife%2C%20and%20I%20worry%20that%20this%20fear%20has%20kept%20you%20from%20being%20honest%20with%20both%20her%20and%20yourself.%20But%20having%20an%20open%20relationship%20doesn't%20just%20mean%20having%20a%20polyamorous%20sex%20life%3B%20it%20also%20means%20being%20open%20and%20honest%20with%20your%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-marriage-partner-moved-in-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742510110000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635800affc29ff001a5f516f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht