ng%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20which%20leases%20were%20removed%20from%20the%20list%2C%20or%20why%2C%20and%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20General%20Services%20Administration%2C%20which%20manages%20federal%20real%20estate%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20removals%20of%20the%20lease%20terminations%20from%20DOGE's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GSA%20previously%20said%20it%20was%20reversing%20over%20100%20lease%20terminations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F03%2F17%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fmusk-doge-lease-terminations.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20%3C%2Fa%3Eearlier%20this%20week.%20When%20reached%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20GSA%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20specific%20numbers%20but%20said%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Bis%20reviewing%20all%20options%20to%20optimize%20the%20federal%20footprint%20and%20building%20utilization%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bsending%20letters%20of%20intent%20to%20customer%20agencies%20to%20inform%20them%20GSA%20is%20considering%20lease%20termination%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bactively%20managing%20lease%20contracts%20by%20leveraging%20existing%20contract%20cancellation%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20in%20instances%20where%20current%20leases%20are%20deemed%20the%20most%20suitable%2C%20the%20GSA%20will%20adjust%20its%20approach%20by%20%26quot%3Beither%20rescinding%20termination%20notices%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20not%20issuing%20them%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20lease%20terminations%20still%20on%20DOGE's%20list%20as%20of%20Thursday%20are%2027%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20buildings%2C%20including%20one%20in%20Newark%2C%20New%20Jersey%20with%20an%20annual%20lease%20of%20over%20%24630%2C000%2C%20which%20DOGE%20says%20without%20providing%20further%20detail%20will%20amount%20to%20over%20%242%20million%20in%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20also%20includes%20buildings%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20National%20Park%20Service%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20other%20federal%20agencies.%20But%20the%20exact%20status%20of%20each%20%26quot%3Blease%20termination%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20clear%20for%20every%20item%20on%20the%20list%20%E2%80%94%20some%20buildings%20include%20as%20much%20detail%20as%20when%20the%20lease%20termination%20was%20sent%20and%20when%20it%20will%20be%20terminated%2C%20while%20others%20are%20simply%20marked%20as%20%26quot%3Btermination%20via%20mass%20mod.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20some%20lawmakers%20have%20found%20success%20pushing%20back%20against%20DOGE's%20attempt%20to%20shut%20down%20their%20state's%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Republican%20Rep.%20Tom%20Cole%20of%20Oklahoma%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcole.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Fcole-statement-national-weather-center-norman-social-security-administration%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20that%20after%20advocating%20for%20several%20federal%20buildings%20in%20his%20state%2C%20DOGE%20agreed%20not%20to%20end%20their%20leases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20working%20closely%20with%20DOGE%20and%20the%20Administration%2C%20I%20am%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20that%20common%20sense%20has%20prevailed%2C%20as%20the%20National%20Weather%20Center%20in%20Norman%2C%20the%20Social%20Security%20Administration%20Office%20in%20Lawton%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Health%20Services%20Office%20in%20Oklahoma%20City%20will%20remain%20operational%20in%20Oklahoma%2C%26quot%3B%20Cole%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Sen.%20Ben%20Ray%20Luj%C3%A1n%20of%20New%20Mexico%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lujan.senate.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Flujan-condemns-potential-closure-of-carlsbad-facility-critical-to-the-mission-of-nations-only-repository-for-the-disposal-of-nuclear-waste%2F%5