0like%20familiarity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20content%20strategy%20can%20be%20summed%20up%20in%20seven%20simple%20words%3A%20If%20it%20ain't%20broke%2C%20don't%20fix%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20string%20of%20creative%20misfires%20at%20the%20box%20office%20during%20former%20CEO%20Bob%20Chapek's%20brief%20tenure%2C%20the%20House%20of%20Mouse%20has%20regained%20its%20mojo%20by%20playing%20the%20hits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Disney's%20most%20successful%20movies%20last%20year%20were%20sequels%20or%20reboots%2C%20as%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20said%20Thursday%20at%20Disney's%20annual%20shareholder%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20produced%20each%20of%20the%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boxofficemojo.com%2Fyear%2Fworld%2F2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighest-grossing%20movies%20of%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BInside%20Out%202%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDeadpool%20%26amp%3B%20Wolverine%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMoana%202.%26quot%3B%20Audiences%20made%20those%20installments%20of%20familiar%20films%20billion-dollar%20blockbusters.%20And%20%26quot%3BMufasa%2C%26quot%3B%20based%20on%201994's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lion%20King%2C%26quot%3B%20fared%20fairly%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIger%20then%20listed%20some%20of%20the%20Disney%20movies%20he's%20most%20excited%20about%20this%20year%3A%20%26quot%3BSnow%20White%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20remake%20of%20the%201937%20classic%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fantastic%20Four%3A%20First%20Steps%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20follows%20earlier%20Fantastic%20Four%20films%20from%2020th%20Century%20Studios%2C%20%26quot%3BZootopia%202%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20third%20%26quot%3BAvatar%26quot%3B%20movie%2C%20and%20a%20live-action%20version%20of%202002's%20%26quot%3BLilo%20%26amp%3B%20Stitch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20all%20old%20hat%20from%20Disney%2C%20as%20Iger%20remarked.%20Marvel%20has%20%26quot%3BThunderbolts*%26quot%3B%20coming%20in%20May%2C%20and%20Pixar%20is%20debuting%20an%20original%20film%20titled%20%26quot%3BElio%26quot%3B%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Disney%20fans%20and%20shareholders%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20this%20clear%20shift%20toward%20safer%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242e51917-1395-4a08-aa2b-69147fa1cace%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafe%20over%20sorry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20question%20for%20Iger%20during%20the%20shareholder%20meeting%20was%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20doing%20to%20prioritize%20the%20importance%20of%20creativity%20across%20the%20company%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIger's%20seemingly%20unscripted%20response%20was%20quite%20telling.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20creativity%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20soaring%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20named%20nine%20titles%2C%20from%20%26quot%3BAvatar%3A%20Fire%20and%20Ash%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BZootopia%202%2C%26quot%3B%20meant%20to%20typify%20Disney's%20creative%20spirit.%20But%20only%20one%20of%20those%20films%20%E2%80%94%20the%20action%20thriller%20%26quot%3BThe%20Amateur%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20brand%20new%20to%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20reasons%20for%20Disney's%20risk%20aversion%2C%20particularly%20at%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20company%20is%20feeling%20the%20pressure%20from%20Wall%20Street.%20Its%20stock%20has%20made%20little%20progress%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20and%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-bob-iger-ceo-successor-early-2026-james-gorman-chairman-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emust%20select%20Iger's%20successor%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20next%20year%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20indicates%20people%20crave%20familiar%20movies%20and%20shows.%20Sequels%20and%20reboots%20require%20little%20explanation%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20cut%20through%20a%20crowded%20and%20cluttered%20media%20landscape%20where%20everyone%20is%20siloed%20in%20their%20own%20algorithms.%20Even%20if%20audiences%20aren't%20fired%20up%20for%20new%20installments%2C%20they%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20remember%20and%20talk%20about%20them%2C%20which%20can%20reduce%20marketing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamiliar%20films%20have%20a%20higher%20floor.%20While%20their%20upside%20might%20not%20be%20the%20same%20as%20a%20new%20breakout%20hit%2C%20they're%20also%20far%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20financial%20flop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20considering%20the%20pressure%20that%20Iger%20and%20Disney%20are%20under%2C%20big%20gambles%20on%20fresh%20ideas%20can%20backfire%20%E2%80%94%20just%20ask%20Chapek%20about%20the%20quickly%20forgotten%20bomb%20%26quot%3BStrange%20World.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22922f1b55-bf1f-46ca-9a77-402ebf6dae7b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAudiences%20want%20comfort%20food%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Hollywood%20may%20pay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20movies%3A%20Disney's%20original%20TV%20shows%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20moving%20the%20needle%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20Disney%2B%20show%20made%20it%20onto%20Nielsen's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nielsen.com%2Finsights%2F2025%2Ftop-streaming-tv-trends-2024-artey-awards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop-10%20ranking%20of%20streaming%20originals%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20LightShed%20Partners%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efound.%20The%20streamer%20did%20have%20the%20chart-topping%20kids'%20show%20%26quot%3BBluey%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it's%20licensed%20to%20Disney%20from%20the%20Australian%20Broadcasting%20Corp.%20What's%20startling%20is%20that%20%26quot%3BBluey%26quot%3B%20made%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flightshedtmt.com%2F2025%2F03%2F06%2Fsurprising-disney-netflix-hulu-amazon-paramount-peacock-streaming-stats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20time%20spent%20with%20the%20streamer%20last%20year%2C%20per%20LightShed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221622%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nielsen%20streaming%20originals%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3