er%20was%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20hospital%20and%20will%20be%20arrested%20later%2C%20the%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20of%20the%20employees%20-%20Shankar%20Shinde%20(63)%2C%20Rajan%20Chavan%20(42)%2C%20Gurudas%20Lokare%20(45)%20and%20Subhash%20Bhosale%20(44)%20-%20died%20as%20they%20were%20sitting%20in%20the%20rear%20and%20could%20not%20open%20the%20emergency%20exit%20door%20in%20time.%20Besides%2C%20six%20passengers%20sustained%20burn%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20probe%20was%20on%2C%20the%20DCP%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742491800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fd0k6dcl8_pune-bus-fire_625x300_19_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fupset-over-salary-cut-driver-started-bus-fire-that-killed-4-in-pune-cops-7970715%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fire%20on%20a%20private%20firm's%20minibus%20that%20killed%20four%20employees%20near%20Pune%20was%20allegedly%20an%20act%20of%20sabotage%20by%20a%20vengeful%20driver%20who%20had%20a%20dispute%20with%20some%20staffers%20and%20was%20also%20upset%20over%20a%20pay%20cut%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Auto%2C%2014%20Children%3A%20Video%20Of%20UP%20Cop's%20Traffic%20Stop%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20cop%20stopped%20an%20autorickshaw%20for%20checking%20at%20an%20intersection%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jhansi.%20The%20police%20officer%20was%20surprised%20when%20he%20saw%2014%20schoolchildren%20travelling%20in%20a%20small%20auto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cop%20posted%20at%20the%20BKD%20intersection%20stopped%20a%20three-wheeler%20when%2