g88dlqlo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kirsty%20Coventry%20Elected%20First%20Woman%20President%20Of%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EZimbabwean%20Kirsty%20Coventry%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20and%20African%20to%20be%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20on%20Thursday%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20moment%26quot%3B.%20At%2041%2C%20the%20two-time%20Olympic%20swimming%20champion%20is%20also%20the%20youngest%20ever%20person%20to%20hold%20the%20most%20powerful%20position%20in%20sports%20governance.%20Coventry%2C%20the%20Zimbabwean%20sports%20minister%2C%20is%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20the%20German%20Thomas%20Bach%2C%20who%20steps%20down%20as%20IOC%20supremo%20after%2012%20years.%20She%20told%20her%20fellow%20IOC%20members%20she%20would%20work%20with%20the%20six%20other%20heavyweight%20rivals%20she%20beat%20in%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20extraordinary%20moment.%20As%20a%20nine-year-old%20girl%20I%20never%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20be%20standing%20up%20here%20one%20day%2C%20getting%20to%20give%20back%20to%20this%20incredible%20movement%20of%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Coventry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20a%20huge%20honour%20but%20it%20is%20a%20reminder%20to%20every%20single%20one%20of%20you%20that%20I%20will%20lead%20this%20organisation%20with%20so%20much%20pride%2C%20with%20the%20values%20at%20the%20core%20and%20I%20will%20make%20all%20of%20you%20very%2C%20very%20proud%20and%2C%20I%20hope%2C%20extremely%20confident%20in%20the%20decision%20you've%20taken%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20heart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoventry%2C%20who%20was%20strongly%20believed%20to%20be%20Bach's%20favoured%20candidate%2C%20was%20thought%20to%20be%20in%20a%20tight-run%20race%20with%20IOC%20veteran%20Juan%20Antonio%20Samaranch%20Junior%20and%20World%20Athletics%20chief%20Sebastian%20Coe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20general%20surprise%20the%20race%20was%20decided%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoventry%20received%2049%20of%20the%2097%20votes%20possible%2C%20with%20Samaranch%20obtaining%2028%20and%20Coe%20third%20with%20a%20humbling%20eight%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamaranch%20was%20bidding%20to%20emulate%20his%20father%20of%20the%20same%20name%20who%20led%20the%20Olympic%20movement%20for%2021%20years%20and%20World%20Athletics%20president%20Coe%20was%20seeking%20to%20become%20the%20first%20Briton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20both%2C%20their%20dreams%20of%20being%20IOC%20president%20one%20day%20are%20over%2C%20owing%20to%20their%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESki%20federation%20chief%20Johan%20Eliasch%2C%20Morinari%20Watanabe%2C%20president%20of%20the%20international%20gymnastics%20federation%2C%20cycling%20head%20David%20Lappartient%20and%20Prince%20Feisal%20al-Hussein%20were%20the%20other%20four%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20that%20quartet%20garnered%20more%20than%20four%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Geopolitical%20hurdles%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Bach%20refused%20to%20be%20drawn%20on%20whether%20he%20backed%20Coventry%2C%20saying%20only%20that%20a%20new%20era%20%26quot%3Brequires%20new%20leaders%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20she%20fought%20a%20low-key%20media%20campaign%20compared%20to%20Coe%20and%20Samaranch%20Junior%2C%20her%20lobbying%20was%20so%20effective%20that%20one%20seriously%20ill%20member%20specifically%20flew%20to%20Greece%20to%20vote%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20had%20been%20raised%20about%20Coventry%20being%20a%20minister%20in%20a%20Zimbabwean%20government%20whose%20election%20in%202023%20was%20declared%20undemocratic%20and%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20made%20little%20impact%20with%20her%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoventry%20faces%20enormous%20geopolitical%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20dealing%20with%20unpredictable%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20with%20Los%20Angeles%20hosting%20the%202028%20Summer%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoventry%20said%20during%20her%20campaign%20that%20if%20she%20won%20it%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20moment%20for%20Africa%20as%20it%20would%20show%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20ready%20to%20lead%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20will%20take%20over%20a%20financially%20secure%20IOC%20but%20those%20calm%20waters%20are%20muddied%20by%20a%20febrile%20geopolitical%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamaranch%20Junior%20had%20argued%20that%20in%20this%20%26quot%3Bvery%20complex%20world%26quot%3B%2C%20where%20previously%20undisputed%20truths%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Buniversality%2C%20fraternity%20and%20unity%26quot%3B%20are%20now%20questioned%2C%20it%20was%20no%20time%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20in%20the%20dark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2065-year-old%20Spaniard%2C%20an%20assured%20and%20polished%20performer%2C%20congratulated%20Coventry%20and%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20going%20anywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20good%20news%2C%20the%20IOC%20is%20moving%20into%20the%20future%2C%20she%20has%20so%20much%20support%20from%20the%20membership%2C%20we%20will%20all%20walk%20behind%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoe%20appeared%20to%20be%20seen%20by%20Bach%20as%20the%20disruptor%20candidate%2C%20which%20is%20perhaps%20surprising%20given%20many%20would%20view%20him%20as%20an%20establishment%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20low%20score%20will%20be%20a%20bitter%20blow%20to%20the%20two-time%201%2C500%20metres%20Olympic%20champion%20who%20is%20accustomed%20to%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoe%2C%2068%2C%20became%20a%20lawmaker%20for%20the%20centre-right%20Conservatives%20and%20led%20London's%20successful%20bid%20to%20host%20the%202012%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20oversaw%20the%20highly-praised%20hosting%20of%20those%20Olympics%20and%20has%20been%20credited%20with%20reforming%20track%20and%20field's%20global%20body%20since%20becoming%20president%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20problems%20the%20new%20president%20will%20face%20will%20be%20the%20return%20to%20the%20Olympic%20fold%20of%20Russia.%20In%20Paris%20last%20year%20their%20athletes%20were%20forced%20to%20competed%20under%20a%20neutral%20banner%2C%20owing%20to%20the%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742490420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frmtd2l5g_kirsty-coventry-afp_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics%2Fkirsty-coventry-elected-first-woman-president-of-international-olympic-committee-7970455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22International%20Olympic%20Committee%20on%20Thursday%20declaring%20it%20to%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20moment.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samay%20cancels%20India%20tour%20after%203rd%20summon%20from%20Cyber%20Cell%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742490209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119266511%2Cimgsize-13058.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsamay-raina-cancels-india-tour-after-third-summon-from-maharashtra-cyber-cell-over-indias-got-latent-controversy-issues-refunds%2Farticleshow%2F119266528.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119266528.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EStand-up%20comedian%20Samay%20Raina%20has%20shared%20an%20important%20update%2