03%2C50%2C000%20per%20month%20as%20opposed%20to%20Rs%202%2C50%2C000%20per%20month%20earlier%3B%20this%20does%20not%20include%20a%20proposed%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20month%20(up%20from%20Rs%2040%2C000%20per%20month)%20for%20travel%20in%20their%20respective%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20allowances%2C%20telephone%20charges%2C%20and%20postal%20charges%20could%20increase%20from%20the%20current%20Rs%2085%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%2C10%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20also%20proposes%20a%2067%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20salaries%20for%20the%20Assembly%20Speaker%20and%20Legislative%20Council%20Chairman%20-%20from%20Rs%2075%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%2C25%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20'sumptuary%20allowances'%20could%20also%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%205%2C00%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20their%20House%20Rent%20Allowances%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20Chief%20Whips%20of%20the%20treasury%20and%20opposition%20benches%2C%20could%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%202%2C50%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20deputies%20could%20also%20see%20pay%20hikes%3B%20salaries%20may%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increased%20pay%20proposals%20have%2C%20however%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20opposition%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%C2%A0%20pointed%20to%20what%20they%20say%20is%20the%20poor%20condition%20of%20the%20state%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20even%20a%20member%20of%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20has%20raised%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Bengaluru%3A%20On%20the%20salary%20hike%20proposed%20for%20Karnataka%20MLAs%2C%20Congress%20MLA%20Dr%20Ranganath%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B%20I%20am%20not%2