has%20also%20paid%20Rs%2040%20million%20in%20taxes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurtaza%20added%20that%20PCB%20chief%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20revising%20the%20fiscal%20targets%2C%20showing%20active%20involvement%20in%20improving%20the%20board's%20financial%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20PCB%20had%20several%20financial%20investments%20and%20that%20the%20budget%20for%20stadium%20upgrades%20was%20set%20at%20Rs%2018%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Phase%20one%20of%20the%20project%2C%20Rs%2012%20billion%20was%20allocated%2C%20and%20Rs%2010.5%20billion%20has%20already%20been%20spent%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20remaining%20funds%20will%20be%20used%20to%20further%20improve%20these%20and%20other%20stadiums%2C%20including%20those%20in%20Karachi%2C%20Faisalabad%2C%20and%20Rawalpindi%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Murtaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CFO%20said%20that%20the%20PCB%20had%20completed%20major%20renovations%20in%20just%20four%20months%2C%20ensuring%20that%20venues%20now%20meet%20international%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%2029%20years%2C%20a%20major%20stadium%20upgrade%20project%20was%20undertaken%2C%20which%20was%20a%20significant%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20Mir%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20reduction%20in%20salaries%20of%20domestic%20men's%20and%20women's%20players%2C%20Mir%20said%20Chairman%20Naqvi%20had%20reversed%20the%20decision%20to%20cut%20their%20salaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20PCB's%20absence%20from%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20the%20officials%20said%20they%20are%20still%20awaiting%20a%20full%20explanation%20from%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurtaza%20said%20very%20soon%20the%20PCB%20would%20make%20available%20all%20its%20financial%20details%20relating%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20on%20the%20Board's%20official%20website%20for%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except