March%2013%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Flifestyle%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-problems%2Fsilent-killer-21yo-pt-and-mma-fighter-dies-in-melbourne-following-intense-exercise%2Fnews-story%2F0f34a64c921d8027aeabd3c2ac8c1ce9%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20family%20said%20he%20fought%20and%20underwent%20multiple%20surgeries.%20However%2C%20after%20spending%20days%20in%20an%20induced%20coma%2C%20the%20doctors%20told%20the%20family%20to%20say%20goodbye%20as%20did%20not%20know%20if%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20save%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20got%20into%20the%20ICU%2C%20the%20doctor%20said%20when%20they%20opened%20him%20up%20again%20(in%20another%20emergency%20surgery)%20there%20was%20just%20too%20much%20tissue%20that%20had%20died%20and%20there%20was%20so%20much%20damage%2C%20there%20was%20nothing%20more%20they%20could%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Jake's%20mother%20Sharone%20Sendler%20told%20news.com.au.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%20to%20him%2C%20'it's%20OK%20baby%2C%20you%20can%20rest%20now%2C%20you%20fought%20so%20hard'%20and%20I%20kissed%20him%20on%20the%20forehead%20and%20he%20passed%20away.%20It%20was%20the%20worst%20moment%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stuff.co.nz%2Fsport%2F360623066%2Faustralian-mma-fighter-dies-rare-condition-linked-intense-gym-workouts%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Stuff%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20doctors%20said%20it%20was%20the%20most%20severe%20case%20of%20rhabdomyolysis%20they%20had%20ever%20encountered.%20Rhabdomyolysis%20is%20a%20breakdown%20of%20muscle%20tissue%2C%20which%20releases%20a%20toxin%20into%20the%20bloodstream%20and%20can%20cause%20kidney%20failure.%20It%20can%20also%20cause%20serious%20problems%20with%20the%20heart%20and%20other%20organs.%20Symptoms%20include%20muscle%20pain%2C%20exhaustion%20and%20dark%20urine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3